.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-FEE-BASE-SKEWNESS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-fee-base-skewness \- FEAT-2802 skewness of fee_base_msat across channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-fee-base-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes skewness of fee_base_msat across channels for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2802).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBfee_base_skewness\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
